section.section:
"Contract" includes an agreement for:
The erection, repair, rebuilding, or improvement of a building;
The drilling and installation of wells to supply water;
The construction or installation of any swimming pool or fencing;
The grading, filling, landscaping, and paving of the premises;
The installation of waterlines, sanitary sewers, storm drains, or streets; or
The erection, repair, rebuilding, or improvement of a wharf.
